{
  "stem": "3848.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And the name was, which was my mother's name, Gresores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "So from there on I became Greshe Gresores.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Gresores.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Now we had to go back into Russia deep, but we landed in Jambul.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "It was a big city in Kazakhstan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Over there, the undercover there, the KGB again surrounded when they saw men on the streets, they picked them up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And my uncle and I were picked up again on the market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "We were looking for something, for some food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "They picked us up and they sent us to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And they called it a Trudovaya armyia, which is our army for work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And they sent us to a kolkhoz not far from Jambul, I would say about 30 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And the kolkhoz, was-- the name of it was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Emini ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Molotov. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Molotov. ?] That was the foreign minister's name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A kolkhoz is a collective farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to help them work on the fields until something happened over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That two Polish guys, they were working there for some kind of iron works, and one of them killed a Kazak in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were afraid of us, all the people, the native people from that kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had to-- they kicked us out from that kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't want us there anymore because they didn't know who was the one that killed that particular woman, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went back to Jambul from over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Jambul, I found a friend that was a-- he was from Lvov.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Isaac [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
